txt.en: Wanted: Tough sword sheaths from brigands and half-orcs in Cardolan. In addition, those who dare to brave Tyrn Gorthad might also recover these from barrow-wights. Those who deliver these trophies will receive modest compensation from the Dúnedain of Cardolan.
